VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(secret|apikey|token|password)\s*[:=]\s*"[^"]{8,}"
WHEN EXPR MISSING:os\.Getenv|os\.LookupEnv|viper\.|config\.|vault\. && MISSING:example|test|placeholder|TODO
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects likely hardcoded secrets in Go source/config.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Echo Hardcoded Secret Material.
